2007-04-20  Joseph Myers  <joseph@codesourcery.com>

    Merge from Sourcery G++ binutils 2.17:

    2007-03-20  Joseph Myers  <joseph@codesourcery.com>
    Based on patch by Mark Hatle <mark.hatle@windriver.com>.
